  <verse number="9" style="v" />But stay away from senseless debates, entanglements about Jewish genealogies, arguments and disputes about the religious law. Those are a useless waste of your time and energy. 

  <verse number="10" style="v" />If people insist on engaging in these divisive activities after you have warned them one or two times, then have nothing more to do with them,

  <verse number="11" style="v" />because people like that have turned away from the truth; they live in sin and condemn themselves.</para>
